
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HelloGC Form Visualizer</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74ebd5, #ACB6E5);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #4a90e2;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        input[type="file"],
        input[type="text"] {
            width: 90%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 2px solid #4a90e2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            outline: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        input[type="file"]:focus,
        input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: #2c71b8;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.5);
        }
        input[type="submit"] {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            background: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background: #2c71b8;
        }
        .footer-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Visualise your HTML form with HelloGC!!</p>
        <p>Your input field must have <b>name</b> attributes.</p>
        <p>Example: <code>name="name"</code></p>

        <h1>Hello GC ðŸ‘‹</h1>

        <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <label>Upload your HTML file:</label><br>
            <input type="file" name="file" accept=".html">

            <label>Enter the action of your form:</label><br>
            <input type="text" name="rout" placeholder='If action="/submit" then enter /submit'>

            <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form>

        <p class="footer-note">
            This tool is made by HelloGC. Since it is in the initial stage, there may be some issues.  
            If it doesnâ€™t work, try renaming your file.  
            Thank You!!!
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
